column4: anyone know which IRC channel they discuss the Ubuntu site or Ubuntu wiki at?
(07:42:24 PM) ubottu: <Jack_Sparrow> wants you to know: #ubuntu is the Ubuntu support channel, for all Ubuntu-related support questions. Please use #ubuntu-offtopic for other topics. Thanks!
(07:42:58 PM) mogus: its about the ubuntu wiki - how is not not ubuntu support related?
